<item>
            <title>[SYNAPSE-158] Setting messageType using property mediator to Axis2MC is not effective</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SYNAPSE-158</link>
                <project id="12310201" key="SYNAPSE">Synapse</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Setting the messageType property of the axis2 MC using the property mediator does not set that correctly.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Here is the configuration for setting this property;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;property action=&quot;set&quot; name=&quot;messageType&quot; value=&quot;application/atom+xml&quot; scope=&quot;axis2&quot;/&amp;gt; &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
