                                                                                                                <comments>
                            <comment id="12538443" author="ruwan" created="Mon, 29 Oct 2007 09:49:35 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have fixed this issue. There was a case where one need to set properties in to the client options, and hence I have added the scope &quot;client&quot; to the property mediator which will set the properties on the axis2 message context client options&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12538461" author="ruwan" created="Mon, 29 Oct 2007 11:48:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have changed the scope value from &quot;client&quot; to the &quot;axis2-client&quot; in order for it to be meaning full. (as per asankha&apos;s comment)&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
